data.description: This property is a stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that combines modern comfort with eco-friendly features. This spacious residence spans 1,929 sqft, offering a perfect blend of style and functionality.  As you enter, you'll be greeted by a thoughtfully designed interior that maximizes space and natural light. The four bedrooms provide ample room for relaxation, while the two bathrooms showcase contemporary finishes and fixtures.  One of the standout features of this property is the dedicated RV/boat parking pad, providing convenient storage for your recreational vehicles. Whether you're an outdoor enthusiast or simply seeking extra storage space, this feature adds a valuable dimension to the property.  Embrace sustainable living with the inclusion of solar panels, a forward-thinking addition that not only reduces your carbon footprint but also contributes to energy efficiency. Imagine enjoying the benefits of lower utility bills while knowing you're making a positive impact on the environment.  Located in the desirable Crestview area, this home offers the perfect combination of tranquility and accessibility. The neighborhood is known for its friendly atmosphere and proximity to local amenities, making it an ideal choice for families and individuals alike.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the unique charm this home has to offer.
